  "id": "api/endpoints/custom-actions/listCustomActions",
  "title": "List Custom Actions",
  "type": "api_endpoint",
  "category": "api",
  "content": "# List Custom Actions\n\nReturns a list of Custom Action objects. The list can be optionally filtered and sorted on the server before being returned.\n\n## Endpoint\n\n`POST /custom-actions/list`",
  "summary": "List Custom Actions",
  "source": "openapi.json",
